<!-- Halting Concept -->
<section xml:id="ref.concepts.halt">
	<title>Halting</title>

	<section xml:id="ref.concepts.halt.definition">
		<title>Definition</title>

		<para>
			Execution of an expression is halted if it can not take an autonomous
			step, nor will it ever receive a response to any outstanding site
			call. Therefore, a halted expression will have no further execution.
		</para>
		
		<para>See <link linkend="ref.concepts.states">expression states</link> for further detail.</para>

	</section>

